	(text "Power: USB 5V (logic) + external jack (bus/DUT) OR-ed via D1/D2 to V5RAW; Q1 P-FET switches bus +5V. Soft-start: C10 ramps Q1 gate. DUT rail protected by bulk C9 + TVS clamp D3. Gate pulled to V5RAW (off), pulled low by Q2 NPN when DUT_PWR_EN=1."
